-docs/ai-eval-roadmap.md:10:**Goal:** Build the infrastructure to scientifically validate AI output quality, enable A/B testing of prompts, and measure the metrics that the Manus research identifies as critical (Faithfulness ≥ 0.90, Context Recall ≥ 0.85).
